title: 'JS on Politics' live show every Thursday at noon
text:
'JS on Politics' live show every Thursday at noon Sept. 30, 2015 2:15 p.m. 
Join the Journal Sentinel's panel of journalists as they discuss the latest political news in Wisconsin. We're also taking your questions and comments. Submit them in our live blog or this link's comments or tweet them to us using #jsonpolitics. 
Read and share your thoughts on this story. E-mail Newsletter 
The latest local news delivered to your inbox Monday-Friday around noon – or whenever there’s big breaking news. Enter your e-mail address above and click "Sign Up Now!" to begin receiving your e-mail newsletter Get the Newsletter! Login or Register to manage all your newsletter preferences. Manage all your newsletter preferences. All Politics Blog 
From Madison and around the state, to Washington D.C., a daily dose of political news and glimpses behind the scenes.
